# {{lb|en|countable|uncountable}} The outer pod of the tiny fruit of a number of species in the genus ''[[Zanthoxylum]]'' widely grown and consumed in Asia as a spice. Not closely related to [[black pepper]] or to [[chilli pepper]]s.
# {{lb|en|uncountable}} [[spice|Spice]] made from this pod.
# {{lb|en|countable}} A plant producing the pods, ''Zanthoxylum''

